<%- include('../partials/user/header.ejs') %>

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1>About Chocoluxe</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Crafting Moments of Pure Indulgence</p>
    </div>

    <div class="story-section">
        <div class="story-content">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2020, Chocoluxe was born from a passion for creating exceptional chocolate experiences. Our master chocolatiers combine traditional craftsmanship with innovative techniques to create chocolates that are both visually stunning and extraordinarily delicious.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-image">
            <svg class="chocolate-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="120" height="120">
                <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-9 13H4v-5h7v5zm9 0h-7v-5h7v5zm0-7H4V6h16v4z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="values-section">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-item">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2L1 21h22L12 2zm0 3.83L19.17 19H4.83L12 5.83zM11 16h2v2h-2zm0-6h2v4h-2z" fill="currentColor"/>
                </svg>
                <h3>Quality</h3>
                <p>We source only the finest ingredients from sustainable producers worldwide.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="value-item">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5s-3 1.34-3 3 1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V18h14v-1.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05.02.01.03.03.04.04 1.14.83 1.93 1.94 1.93 3.41V18h6v-1.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z" fill="currentColor"/>
                </svg>
                <h3>Community</h3>
                <p>We believe in building lasting relationships with our customers and partners.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="value-item">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 22c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2h-4c0 1.1.9 2 2 2zm6-6v-5c0-3.07-1.63-5.64-4.5-6.32V4c0-.83-.67-1.5-1.5-1.5s-1.5.67-1.5 1.5v.68C7.64 5.36 6 7.92 6 11v5l-2 2v1h16v-1l-2-2zm-2 1H8v-6c0-2.48 1.51-4.5 4-4.5s4 2.02 4 4.5v6z" fill="currentColor"/>
                </svg>
                <h3>Innovation</h3>
                <p>We constantly explore new flavors and techniques while respecting traditional craftsmanship.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="commitment-section">
        <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>At Chocoluxe, we're committed to creating exceptional chocolate experiences while maintaining sustainable and ethical practices. Every piece of chocolate we craft tells a story of passion, innovation, and dedication to quality.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
.about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
}

.hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dark) 0%, var(--primary) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

.hero-section h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.hero-section .tagline {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

.story-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
}

.story-content h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.story-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
}

.chocolate-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
}

.values-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.values-section h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
}

.value-item {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--background);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
}

.value-item svg {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.value-item h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.commitment-section {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.commitment-section h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-section {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .values-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
}
</style>

